    "title": "Senior Frontend Developer at DeHaat International Enterprises",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at DeHaat International Enterprises. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Frontend Developer to strengthen our Kochi-based team.\n\nAbout DeHaat International Enterprises:\nDeHaat International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Python\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DeHaat International Enterprises!",
